{"tid":910497,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地疑犯「便急」大鬧醫院　鎖手銬仍能扯斷解犯鏈","createTime":"2018-11-21T08:36:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-21T11:43:14.000Z","uid":75969,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"94493a3bcc11885d8fffec9d1bec99458d53bc6f","tid":910497,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:36:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001_01p.jpg?20181121143506\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20181121143506&h=0e01b1ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">疑犯在醫院期間，全程被鎖上手銬及鐵鏈。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/photo/bkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001_03p.jpg?20181121143506\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001_03p.jpg%3F20181121143506&h=d73a7dc5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">解犯鏈被弄斷。</span><br />\n<br />\n一名姓李(30歲)持雙程證內地男子，周一晚(19日)9時許，在荃灣如心廣場一間酒店，疑因帳單數目有出入，與職員理論並發生爭執，酒店保安員介入了解，惟有人突然情緒失控，毀爛職員的對講機，同時又扯斷枱上的電線，有人更與酒店保安員有肢體衝突，酒店職員見狀，無奈報警求助。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報趕至，迅即控制場面，經初步調查後拘捕李，他報稱不適，由警員押送下由救護車送往仁濟醫院治理，其後在醫院南翼11樓急症科病房留醫，期間他雙手被鎖上手銬，腰纏鐵鏈繫在病床。<br />\n<br />\n至昨晨(20日)7時許，據悉李聲稱人有三急，要落床去廁所大便，看守的警員遂向護士要來一個「大便兜」讓其解決，惟有人拒絕兼大吵大嚷，拖着繫在病床的鐵鏈，強行落床逕自前往洗手間，期間有人弄毀解犯鏈及大門，警員見狀即時制止，同時要求上峰增援，最後衝鋒隊警員趕至，合力將疑犯制服，案件交由荃灣警區重案組跟進。疑犯涉嫌2項刑事毀壞及一項普通襲擊，今日(21日)被押往西九龍裁判法院應訊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181121%2Fbkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001.html&d=bSqfC3QsucwX7RxuYEpRAQKEmdudW1rq3V1Y15kzxIU%3D&h=80f7323c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181121/bkn-20181121000416721-1121_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"687963f5c895c24730b0d4985b6c3db038ccc5d3","tid":910497,"uid":1166,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:38:28.000Z","msg":"條鏈淘返黎架？"},{"pid":"04368cece6c24ee6370fc417ad61fbb26df9a46b","tid":910497,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:39:31.000Z","msg":"淋病至愛既支那專才又立奇功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b774f0b02773d781283e4b3bec95c458db483f","tid":910497,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:42:50.000Z","msg":"整爛條鏈行去厠所<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f116de38348a142fbb13df4684ffeb9897fe2ce","tid":910497,"uid":11148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:47:22.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係就地柯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63a30befbb3177db3e59bed425dcf4565573d5d5","tid":910497,"uid":189109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:47:53.000Z","msg":"想問一句，瀨咗未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39f28b623cb8c4e4015ae65e5ad3c494e13ee7d7","tid":910497,"uid":2373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-21T08:48:55.000Z","msg":"香港警察無鏈用"},{"pid":"f52f77201372c86fb7bf69005d81ed07734d1931","tid":910497,"uid":70523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018